---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { config } from "../config";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Võtting Grupp OÜ handles your data and protects your privacy.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal mb-12">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-4 block">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Last updated: March 18, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 space-y-8 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            {config.legalName} ("{config.companyName}", "we", "us", "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data.
            This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you visit our website or use our products and services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">2. Data Controller</h2>
          <p>
            The data controller for the purposes of the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) is:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 p-5 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)] text-sm">
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)] font-medium">{config.legalName}</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-1">{config.location}</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
              <a href={`mailto:${config.email}`} class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">{config.email}</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">3. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Contact information</strong> — name, email address, and any information you provide through our contact form or direct correspondence.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Usage data</strong> — information about how you interact with our website, including pages visited, time spent, and browser type.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Transaction data</strong> — payment information processed through third-party providers (Stripe, Gumroad, RapidAPI, Etsy, Fiverr) when you purchase our products.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
          <p>We process your personal data on the following legal bases under GDPR:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Consent</strong> — when you voluntarily submit a contact form or sign up for communications.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Contractual necessity</strong> — to process transactions and deliver purchased products or services.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Legitimate interest</strong> — to improve our website and services, and to protect against fraud.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">5. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Respond to your enquiries and provide customer support</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Process transactions and deliver purchased products</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Improve our website, products, and services</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Send important updates about your purchases or account</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use the following third-party services that may process data:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Stripe</strong> — payment processing</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">GitHub Pages</strong> — website hosting</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">RapidAPI, Gumroad, Etsy, Fiverr</strong> — marketplace platforms for product distribution</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Each third-party service operates under its own privacy policy. We recommend reviewing their policies directly.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected,
            or as required by applicable law. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">8. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
          <p>As we are based in the European Union (Estonia), you have the following rights under GDPR:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
            {["Right of access to your personal data", "Right to rectification of inaccurate data", "Right to erasure ('right to be forgotten')", "Right to restriction of processing", "Right to data portability", "Right to object to processing", "Right to withdraw consent at any time"].map(right => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
                <span>{right}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${config.email}`} class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">{config.email}</a>.
            You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Estonian Data Protection Inspectorate (Andmekaitse Inspektsioon).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">9. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our website uses minimal cookies necessary for functionality. We do not use advertising or tracking cookies.
            Third-party services may set their own cookies in accordance with their respective privacy policies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">10. Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorised access,
            alteration, disclosure, or destruction. All data transmission is encrypted via HTTPS.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">11. International Transfers</h2>
          <p>
            Your data may be processed by third-party services located outside the European Economic Area (EEA).
            Where this occurs, we ensure appropriate safeguards are in place in compliance with GDPR, including
            Standard Contractual Clauses or adequacy decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
            We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <div class="hr-gradient mb-8"></div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related enquiries:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 p-5 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)] text-sm">
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)] font-medium">{config.legalName}</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-1">{config.location}</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
              <a href={`mailto:${config.email}`} class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">{config.email}</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
